Architecture. Barcelona ; New York: Actar-D, 2008. Print.
Peters, Terri, and Brady Peters. Inside Smartgeometry: Expanding the Architectural
Possibilities of Computational Design. Hoboken, NJ: Wiley, 2013. Print.
Burry, Jane, and Mark Burry. The New Mathematics of Architecture. London: Thames &
Hudson, 2012. Print.
Hensel, Michael. Performance-oriented Architecture: Rethinking Architectural Design and
the Built Environment. Chichester: John Wiley & Sons, 2013. Print.
Jabi, Wassim. Parametric Design for Architecture. London: Laurence King, 2013. Print.
Menges, Achim, and Sean Ahlquist. Computational Design Thinking. Hoboken, NJ: Wiley,
2013. Print.
