備註 Remarks
     The course will be organized into two parts:
1. Further investigation of advanced parametric design tools and concepts such as
cellular packing, minimal surfaces, recursion, mesh geometry etc.
2. The design and prototyping of performative parametricbuilding components through
the design and application of interactive systems.




