課程概述 Course Description
       This course will introduce advanced parametric design topics and develop the students' ability to effectively use parametric design tools and interactive systems to crete functional prototypes of performative building components. 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
Parametric design exploration as instrument of form finding + rationalization.Applying parametric design practices to real world situations.Research the potential for the integration of performative parametric systems. 

